text: The Armtech C30R was an assault rifle concept using 5.56mm (Quadrant with 3.56g standard M193 bullet, dimensions of the rectangular ammunition 35.7×15.8×9.5 mm) similar to the H&K; G11.Jane's Infantry Weapons 1986, ==See also== * Heckler & Koch G11 * Gyrojet * Steyr ACR * Benelli CB M2 * Voere VEC-91 * Lightweight Small Arms Technologies * List of bullpup firearms * List of assault rifles ==References== Category:5.56 mm assault rifles Category:Bullpup rifles Category:Trial and research firearms of Australia Category:Caseless firearms
title: Armtech C30R
